MIPS: kernel: cps-vec: Replace KSEG0 with CKSEG0

In preparation for 64-bit CPS support, we replace KSEG0 with CKSEG0
so 64-bit kernels can be supported.

Cc: <stable@vger.kernel.org> # 3.16+
